The paper proposes a framework for runtime verification of complex systems, including cyber-physical systems, using algebraic structures. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Software Engineering (cs.SE), Programming Languages (cs.PL), Robotics (cs.RO), and Systems and Control (cs.SY). However, given the focus on formal methods and verification, cs.LO is the most likely category. The paper also discusses case studies from the automotive domain, which could suggest a connection to cs.RO or cs.SY.
